#. <section class="sutta" id="an7.56"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.56:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.56:0.2"
msgid "6. Abyākatavagga"
msgstr "6. The Undeclared Points"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 56. Tissabrahmāsutta → tissabrahmasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an7.56:0.3"
msgid "56. Tissabrahmāsutta"
msgstr "56. Tissa the Brahmā"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli4.75"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an7.56:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

msgctxt "an7.56:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati gijjhakūṭe pabbate."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Rājagaha, on the Vulture’s Peak "
"Mountain."

msgctxt "an7.56:1.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho dve devatā abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇā kevalakappaṃ "
"gijjhakūṭaṃ obhāsetvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhaṃsu. Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho ekā devatā "
"bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then, late at night, a glorious deity, lighting up the entire Vulture’s "
"Peak, went up to the Buddha, bowed, stood to one side, and said to him:"

# A curious story, but it seems as if the nuns are actually present.
msgctxt "an7.56:1.4"
msgid "“etā, bhante, bhikkhuniyo vimuttā”ti."
msgstr "“Sir, these nuns are freed!”"

msgctxt "an7.56:1.5"
msgid "Aparā devatā bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "And another deity told the Buddha:"

msgctxt "an7.56:1.6"
msgid "“etā, bhante, bhikkhuniyo anupādisesā suvimuttā”ti."
msgstr "“Sir, these nuns are well freed without anything left over!”"

msgctxt "an7.56:1.7"
msgid "Idamavocuṃ tā devatā."
msgstr "This is what that deity said,"

msgctxt "an7.56:1.8"
msgid "Samanuñño satthā ahosi."
msgstr "and the teacher approved."

msgctxt "an7.56:1.9"
msgid ""
"Atha kho tā devatā “samanuñño satthā”ti bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ "
"katvā tatthevantaradhāyiṃsu."
msgstr ""
"Then that deity, knowing that the teacher approved, bowed and respectfully "
"circled the Buddha, keeping him on his right, before vanishing right there."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an7.56:2.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā tassā rattiyā accayena bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr ""
"Then, when the night had passed, the Buddha told the mendicants all that had "
"happened."

msgctxt "an7.56:2.2"
msgid ""
"“imaṃ, bhikkhave, rattiṃ dve devatā abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇā "
"kevalakappaṃ gijjhakūṭaṃ obhāsetvā yenāhaṃ tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā "
"maṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhaṃsu. Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho, bhikkhave, ekā "
"devatā maṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.56:2.3"
msgid "‘etā, bhante, bhikkhuniyo vimuttā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.56:2.4"
msgid "Aparā devatā maṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.56:2.5"
msgid "‘etā, bhante, bhikkhuniyo anupādisesā suvimuttā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.56:2.6"
msgid "Idamavocuṃ, bhikkhave, tā devatā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.56:2.7"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvā maṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā tatthevantaradhāyiṃsū”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an7.56:3.1"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā mahāmoggallāno bhagavato avidūre nisinno hoti."
msgstr ""
"Now, at that time Venerable Mahāmoggallāna was sitting not far from the "
"Buddha."

msgctxt "an7.56:3.2"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmato mahāmoggallānassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "He thought:"

msgctxt "an7.56:3.3"
msgid "“katamesānaṃ kho devānaṃ evaṃ ñāṇaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "“Which gods know whether a person has anything left over or not?”"

msgctxt "an7.56:3.4"
msgid "‘saupādisese vā saupādisesoti, anupādisese vā anupādiseso’”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.56:3.5"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena tisso nāma bhikkhu adhunākālaṅkato aññataraṃ "
"brahmalokaṃ upapanno hoti."
msgstr ""
"Now, at that time a monk called Tissa had recently passed away and been "
"reborn in a Brahmā realm."

msgctxt "an7.56:3.6"
msgid "Tatrāpi naṃ evaṃ jānanti:"
msgstr "There they knew that"

msgctxt "an7.56:3.7"
msgid "“tisso brahmā mahiddhiko mahānubhāvo”ti."
msgstr "Tissa the Brahmā was very mighty and powerful."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli4.76"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an7.56:4.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno—seyyathāpi nāma balavā puriso samiñjitaṃ vā "
"bāhaṃ pasāreyya, pasāritaṃ vā bāhaṃ samiñjeyya; evamevaṃ—gijjhakūṭe pabbate "
"antarahito tasmiṃ brahmaloke pāturahosi."
msgstr ""
"And then Venerable Mahāmoggallāna, as easily as a strong person would extend "
"or contract their arm, vanished from the Vulture’s Peak and reappeared in "
"that Brahmā realm."

msgctxt "an7.56:4.2"
msgid ""
"Addasā kho tisso brahmā āyasmantaṃ mahāmoggallānaṃ dūratova āgacchantaṃ."
msgstr "Tissa saw Moggallāna coming off in the distance,"

msgctxt "an7.56:4.3"
msgid "Disvā āyasmantaṃ mahāmoggallānaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "and said to him:"

msgctxt "an7.56:4.4"
msgid "“ehi kho, mārisa moggallāna;"
msgstr "“Come, my good Moggallāna!"

msgctxt "an7.56:4.5"
msgid "svāgataṃ, mārisa moggallāna."
msgstr "Welcome, my good Moggallāna!"

msgctxt "an7.56:4.6"
msgid ""
"Cirassaṃ kho, mārisa moggallāna, imaṃ pariyāyamakāsi, yadidaṃ idhāgamanāya."
msgstr "It’s been a long time since you took the opportunity to come here."

msgctxt "an7.56:4.7"
msgid "Nisīda, mārisa moggallāna, idamāsanaṃ paññattan”ti."
msgstr "Sit, my good Moggallāna, this seat is for you.”"

msgctxt "an7.56:4.8"
msgid "Nisīdi kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno paññatte āsane."
msgstr "Moggallāna sat down on the seat spread out."

msgctxt "an7.56:4.9"
msgid ""
"Tissopi kho brahmā āyasmantaṃ mahāmoggallānaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi."
msgstr "Then Tissa bowed to Moggallāna and sat to one side."

msgctxt "an7.56:4.10"
msgid ""
"Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho tissaṃ brahmānaṃ āyasmā mahāmoggallāno etadavoca:"
msgstr "Moggallāna said to him:"

msgctxt "an7.56:4.11"
msgid "“katamesānaṃ kho, tissa, devānaṃ evaṃ ñāṇaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "“Which gods know whether a person has anything left over or not?”"

msgctxt "an7.56:4.12"
msgid "‘saupādisese vā saupādisesoti, anupādisese vā anupādiseso’”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.56:4.13"
msgid "“Brahmakāyikānaṃ kho, mārisa moggallāna, devānaṃ evaṃ ñāṇaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "“The gods of Brahmā’s Group know this.”"

msgctxt "an7.56:4.14"
msgid "‘saupādisese vā saupādisesoti, anupādisese vā anupādiseso’”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an7.56:5.1"
msgid "“Sabbesaññeva kho, tissa, brahmakāyikānaṃ devānaṃ evaṃ ñāṇaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "“But do all of them know this?”"

msgctxt "an7.56:5.2"
msgid "‘saupādisese vā saupādisesoti, anupādisese vā anupādiseso’”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.56:5.3"
msgid ""
"“Na kho, mārisa moggallāna, sabbesaṃ brahmakāyikānaṃ devānaṃ evaṃ ñāṇaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "“No, my good Moggallāna, not all of them."

msgctxt "an7.56:5.4"
msgid "‘saupādisese vā saupādisesoti, anupādisese vā anupādiseso’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli4.77"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an7.56:6.1"
msgid ""
"Ye kho te, mārisa moggallāna, brahmakāyikā devā brahmena āyunā santuṭṭhā "
"brahmena vaṇṇena brahmena sukhena brahmena yasena brahmena ādhipateyyena "
"santuṭṭhā, te uttari nissaraṇaṃ yathābhūtaṃ nappajānanti."
msgstr ""
"Those gods of Brahmā’s Group who are content with the lifespan of Brahmā, "
"with the beauty, happiness, fame, and authority of Brahmā, and who don’t "
"truly understand any higher escape:"

msgctxt "an7.56:6.2"
msgid "Tesaṃ na evaṃ ñāṇaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "they don’t know this."

msgctxt "an7.56:6.3"
msgid "‘saupādisese vā saupādisesoti, anupādisese vā anupādiseso’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.56:6.4"
msgid ""
"Ye ca kho te, mārisa moggallāna, brahmakāyikā devā brahmena āyunā "
"asantuṭṭhā, brahmena vaṇṇena brahmena sukhena brahmena yasena brahmena "
"ādhipateyyena asantuṭṭhā, te ca uttari nissaraṇaṃ yathābhūtaṃ pajānanti."
msgstr ""
"But those gods of Brahmā’s Group who are not content with the lifespan of "
"Brahmā, with the beauty, happiness, fame, and authority of Brahmā, and who "
"do truly understand a higher escape:"

msgctxt "an7.56:6.5"
msgid "Tesaṃ evaṃ ñāṇaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "they do know this."

msgctxt "an7.56:6.6"
msgid "‘saupādisese vā saupādisesoti, anupādisese vā anupādiseso’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an7.56:7.1"
msgid "Idha, mārisa moggallāna, bhikkhu ubhatobhāgavimutto hoti."
msgstr "Take a mendicant who is freed both ways."

msgctxt "an7.56:7.2"
msgid "Tamenaṃ te devā evaṃ jānanti:"
msgstr "The gods know of them:"

msgctxt "an7.56:7.3"
msgid "‘ayaṃ kho āyasmā ubhatobhāgavimutto."
msgstr "‘This venerable is freed both ways."

msgctxt "an7.56:7.4"
msgid "Yāvassa kāyo ṭhassati tāva naṃ dakkhanti devamanussā."
msgstr "As long as their body remains they will be seen by gods and humans."

msgctxt "an7.56:7.5"
msgid "Kāyassa bhedā na naṃ dakkhanti devamanussā’ti."
msgstr "But when their body breaks up gods and men will see them no more.’"

msgctxt "an7.56:7.6"
msgid "Evampi kho, mārisa moggallāna, tesaṃ devānaṃ ñāṇaṃ hoti:"
msgstr ""
"This too is how those gods know whether a person has anything left over or "
"not."

msgctxt "an7.56:7.7"
msgid "‘saupādisese vā saupādisesoti, anupādisese vā anupādiseso’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an7.56:8.1"
msgid "Idha pana, mārisa moggallāna, bhikkhu paññāvimutto hoti."
msgstr "Take a mendicant who is freed by wisdom."

msgctxt "an7.56:8.2"
msgid "Tamenaṃ te devā evaṃ jānanti:"
msgstr "The gods know of them:"

msgctxt "an7.56:8.3"
msgid "‘ayaṃ kho āyasmā paññāvimutto."
msgstr "‘This venerable is freed by wisdom."

msgctxt "an7.56:8.4"
msgid "Yāvassa kāyo ṭhassati tāva naṃ dakkhanti devamanussā."
msgstr "As long as their body remains they will be seen by gods and humans."

msgctxt "an7.56:8.5"
msgid "Kāyassa bhedā na naṃ dakkhanti devamanussā’ti."
msgstr "But when their body breaks up gods and men will see them no more.’"

msgctxt "an7.56:8.6"
msgid "Evampi kho, mārisa moggallāna, tesaṃ devānaṃ ñāṇaṃ hoti:"
msgstr ""
"This too is how those gods know whether a person has anything left over or "
"not."

msgctxt "an7.56:8.7"
msgid "‘saupādisese vā saupādisesoti, anupādisese vā anupādiseso’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an7.56:9.1"
msgid "Idha pana, mārisa moggallāna, bhikkhu kāyasakkhī hoti."
msgstr "Take a mendicant who is a direct witness."

msgctxt "an7.56:9.2"
msgid "Tamenaṃ devā evaṃ jānanti:"
msgstr "The gods know of them:"

msgctxt "an7.56:9.3"
msgid "‘ayaṃ kho āyasmā kāyasakkhī."
msgstr "‘This venerable is a direct witness."

# BB has “spiritual faculties”, but given that the former two clauses relate to sila, I feel sense faculties are meant here. In which case, guiding makes better sense than harmonizing.
msgctxt "an7.56:9.4"
msgid ""
"Appeva nāma ayamāyasmā anulomikāni senāsanāni paṭisevamāno kalyāṇamitte "
"bhajamāno indriyāni samannānayamāno—"
msgstr ""
"Hopefully this venerable will frequent appropriate lodgings, associate with "
"good friends, and control their faculties."

msgctxt "an7.56:9.5"
msgid ""
"yassatthāya kulaputtā sammadeva agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajanti, tadanuttaraṃ—"
"brahmacariyapariyosānaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā "
"upasampajja vihareyyā’ti."
msgstr ""
"Then they might realize the supreme culmination of the spiritual path in "
"this very life, and live having achieved with their own insight the goal for "
"which people from good families rightly go forth from the lay life to "
"homelessness.’ "

msgctxt "an7.56:9.6"
msgid "Evampi kho, mārisa moggallāna, tesaṃ devānaṃ ñāṇaṃ hoti:"
msgstr ""
"This too is how those gods know whether a person has anything left over or "
"not."

msgctxt "an7.56:9.7"
msgid "‘saupādisese vā saupādisesoti, anupādisese vā anupādiseso’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli4.78"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an7.56:10.1"
msgid "Idha pana, mārisa moggallāna, bhikkhu diṭṭhippatto hoti … pe …"
msgstr "Take a mendicant who is attained to view. …"

msgctxt "an7.56:10.2"
msgid "saddhāvimutto hoti … pe …"
msgstr "freed by faith …"

msgctxt "an7.56:10.3"
msgid "dhammānusārī hoti."
msgstr "a follower of the teachings …"

msgctxt "an7.56:10.4"
msgid "Tamenaṃ te devā evaṃ jānanti:"
msgstr "The gods know of them:"

msgctxt "an7.56:10.5"
msgid "‘ayaṃ kho āyasmā dhammānusārī."
msgstr "‘This venerable is a follower of the teachings."

msgctxt "an7.56:10.6"
msgid ""
"Appeva nāma ayamāyasmā anulomikāni senāsanāni paṭisevamāno kalyāṇamitte "
"bhajamāno indriyāni samannānayamāno—"
msgstr ""
"Hopefully this venerable will frequent appropriate lodgings, associate with "
"good friends, and control their faculties."

msgctxt "an7.56:10.7"
msgid ""
"yassatthāya kulaputtā sammadeva agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajanti, tadanuttaraṃ—"
"brahmacariyapariyosānaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā "
"upasampajja vihareyyā’ti."
msgstr ""
"Then they might realize the supreme culmination of the spiritual path in "
"this very life, and live having achieved with their own insight the goal for "
"which people from good families rightly go forth from the lay life to "
"homelessness.’ "

msgctxt "an7.56:10.8"
msgid "Evampi kho, mārisa moggallāna, tesaṃ devānaṃ ñāṇaṃ hoti:"
msgstr ""
"This too is how those gods know whether a person has anything left over or "
"not.”"

msgctxt "an7.56:10.9"
msgid "‘saupādisese vā saupādisesoti, anupādisese vā anupādiseso’”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an7.56:11.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno tissassa brahmuno bhāsitaṃ abhinanditvā "
"anumoditvā—seyyathāpi nāma balavā puriso samiñjitaṃ vā bāhaṃ pasāreyya, "
"pasāritaṃ vā bāhaṃ samiñjeyya; evamevaṃ—brahmaloke antarahito gijjhakūṭe "
"pabbate pāturahosi."
msgstr ""
"Moggallāna approved and agreed with what Tissa the Brahmā said. Then, as "
"easily as a strong person would extend or contract their arm, he vanished "
"from the Brahmā realm and reappeared on the Vulture’s Peak."

msgctxt "an7.56:11.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi."
msgstr "Then Mahāmoggallāna went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side,"

msgctxt "an7.56:11.3"
msgid ""
"Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno yāvatako ahosi tissena brahmunā "
"saddhiṃ kathāsallāpo taṃ sabbaṃ bhagavato ārocesi."
msgstr "and told him what had happened."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "an7.56:12.1"
msgid ""
"“Na hi pana te, moggallāna, tisso brahmā sattamaṃ animittavihāriṃ puggalaṃ "
"deseti”."
msgstr ""
"“But Moggallāna, Tissa the Brahmā didn’t teach the seventh person, the "
"signless meditator.”"

msgctxt "an7.56:12.2"
msgid "“Etassa, bhagavā, kālo, etassa, sugata, kālo."
msgstr "“Now is the time, Blessed One! Now is the time, Holy One!"

msgctxt "an7.56:12.3"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ bhagavā sattamaṃ animittavihāriṃ puggalaṃ deseyya. Bhagavato sutvā "
"bhikkhū dhāressantī”ti."
msgstr ""
"May the Buddha teach the seventh person, the signless meditator. The "
"mendicants will listen and remember it.”"

msgctxt "an7.56:12.4"
msgid "“Tena hi, moggallāna, suṇāhi, sādhukaṃ manasi karohi; bhāsissāmī”ti."
msgstr "“Well then, Moggallāna, listen and pay close attention, I will speak.”"

msgctxt "an7.56:12.5"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno bhagavato paccassosi."
msgstr "“Yes, sir,” Mahāmoggallāna replied."

msgctxt "an7.56:12.6"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr "The Buddha said this:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli4.79"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "an7.56:13.1"
msgid ""
"“Idha, moggallāna, bhikkhu sabbanimittānaṃ amanasikārā animittaṃ "
"cetosamādhiṃ upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""
"“Moggallāna, take the case of a mendicant who, not focusing on any signs, "
"enters and remains in the signless immersion of the heart."

msgctxt "an7.56:13.2"
msgid "Tamenaṃ te devā evaṃ jānanti:"
msgstr "The gods know of them:"

msgctxt "an7.56:13.3"
msgid ""
"‘ayaṃ kho āyasmā sabbanimittānaṃ amanasikārā animittaṃ cetosamādhiṃ "
"upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""
"‘This venerable, not focusing on any signs, enters and remains in the "
"signless immersion of the heart."

msgctxt "an7.56:13.4"
msgid ""
"Appeva nāma ayamāyasmā anulomikāni senāsanāni paṭisevamāno kalyāṇamitte "
"bhajamāno indriyāni samannānayamāno—"
msgstr ""
"Hopefully this venerable will frequent appropriate lodgings, associate with "
"good friends, and control their faculties."

msgctxt "an7.56:13.5"
msgid ""
"yassatthāya kulaputtā sammadeva agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajanti, tadanuttaraṃ—"
"brahmacariyapariyosānaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā "
"upasampajja vihareyyā’ti."
msgstr ""
"Then they might realize the supreme culmination of the spiritual path in "
"this very life, and live having achieved with their own insight the goal for "
"which people from good families rightly go forth from the lay life to "
"homelessness.’ "

msgctxt "an7.56:13.6"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, moggallāna, tesaṃ devānaṃ ñāṇaṃ hoti:"
msgstr ""
"This too is how those gods know whether a person has anything left over or "
"not.”"

msgctxt "an7.56:13.7"
msgid "‘saupādisese vā saupādisesoti, anupādisese vā anupādiseso’”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.56:13.8"
